Package com.astrocalculator

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AstroCalculator
    Class dedicated to calculate basic astronomic information concerning Sun and Moon (e.g. sunset/sunrise time and azimuth, moonrise/moonset time, moon phase etc.)
    AstroCalculator.Location
    Auxiliary class describing geographical location (latitude and longitude).
    AstroDateTime
    Class describing date and time for the needs of AstroCalculator class It is used to set date and time for calculations and to return results e.g. sunrise/sunset type etc.
